{"abstract": "An overseas bribery inquiry involving Avon shows how long winding such cases can be, and how the costs of dealing with potential corrupt payments can exceed the punishment, Peter J. Henning writes in White Collar Watch.", "web_url": "https://dealbook.nytimes.com/2014/12/22/foreign-bribery-cases-that-can-drag-on-and-on/", "snippet": "An overseas bribery inquiry involving Avon shows how long winding such cases can be, and how the costs of dealing with potential corrupt payments can exceed the punishment, Peter J. Henning writes in White Collar Watch.", "lead_paragraph": "It is fitting to recall a quote attributed to the famous Chinese General Sun Tzu that the \u201cwheels of justice grind slow but grind fine\u201d as Avon finally resolved an investigation into payments and gifts provided to government officials in China \u2013 some six years after it began. ", "source": "The New York Times", "multimedia": [{"rank": 0, "subtype": "xlarge", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2014/12/23/business/dbpix-avon/dbpix-avon-articleLarge.jpg", "height": 359, "width": 600, "subType": "xlarge", "crop_name": "articleLarge", "legacy": {"xlarge": "images/2014/12/23/business/dbpix-avon/dbpix-avon-articleLarge.jpg", "xlargewidth": 600, "xlargeheight": 359}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "jumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2014/12/23/business/dbpix-avon/dbpix-avon-jumbo.jpg", "height": 612, "width": 1024, "subType": "jumbo", "crop_name": "jumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "superJumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2014/12/23/business/dbpix-avon/dbpix-avon-superJumbo.jpg", "height": 1224, "width": 2048, "subType": "superJumbo", "crop_name": "superJumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "thumbnail", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2014/12/23/business/dbpix-avon/dbpix-avon-thumbStandard.jpg", "height": 75, "width": 75, "subType":